# Runtime env for Docker / docker-compose. Copy to `.env` next to docker-compose.yml
# (that .env is gitignored). These are passed to the container at run time — they
# are NOT baked into the image.
#
# Gmail App Password (16 chars, no spaces): Google Account → Security →
# 2-Step Verification → App passwords.
